  <description>
Adds three new types of sleep accelerators:
One is 2x1 but otherwise functions the same as the vanilla sleep accelerator, and one projects the sleep acceleration effect to a radius of 6 tiles, but has higher build and power cost. The third is a wall-mounted sleep accelerator.
The power cost and effect radius are configurable.
  </description>
